      <title>高盛将美联储 2024 年降息目标从 3 次改为 2 次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/goldman-sachs-changes-fed-call-to-two-cuts-in-2024-from-three</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 的经济学家预计，美联储今年将降息两次，而不是三次，此前周三的报告显示 3 月份消费者价格涨幅超过预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/goldman-sachs-changes-fed-call-to-two-cuts-in-2024-from-three</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:50:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
